#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/Rendering/WebGPU/README.md:92
msgid "Rendering Core Tests"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/Rendering/WebGPU/README.md:94
msgid ""
"To run the `RenderingCore` tests with `VTK::RenderingWebGPU`, edit `vtk."
"module` to link unit tests with `TEST_DEPENDS`:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/Rendering/WebGPU/README.md:96
msgid "Uncomment the module name under `TEST_DEPENDS`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/Rendering/WebGPU/README.md:97
msgid "Rebuild and run the tests (only a few pass currently)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/Rendering/WebGPU/README.md:98
msgid ""
"Set the `VTK_FACTORY_PREFER` environment variable to "
"`RenderingBackend=WebGPU` or pass `--vtk-factory-prefer "
"RenderingBackend=WebGPU` as command line arguments to the test executable."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/Rendering/WebGPU/README.md:100
msgid ""
"export VTK_FACTORY_PREFER=\"RenderingBackend=WebGPU\"\n"
"./bin/vtkRenderingCoreCxxTests Mace -I\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/Rendering/WebGPU/README.md:105
msgid "or"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/Rendering/WebGPU/README.md:107
msgid ""
"./bin/vtkRenderingCoreCxxTests Mace -I --vtk-factory-prefer "
"RenderingBackend=WebGPU\n"
msgstr ""

